1. Basic Test Execution
Run all tests
npx playwright test

Run a specific test file
npx playwright test tests/Login.spec.js

Run a specific test by name
npx playwright test -g "User can login with valid credentials"

2. Browser & Mode Control
Run in headed mode (override config)
npx playwright test --headed

Run only Chromium
npx playwright test --project=chromium

Run Chromium in headed mode
npx playwright test --project=chromium --headed

3. Debugging & Pausing
Run with Playwright Inspector (BEST for debugging)
npx playwright test --debug

Pause execution at page.pause()
await page.pause();

Run with Node debugger (VS Code)
node --inspect-brk ./node_modules/.bin/playwright test

4. Parallelism & Performance
Run tests sequentially
npx playwright test --workers=1

Run fully parallel
npx playwright test --workers=4

Disable retries
npx playwright test --retries=0

5. CI / Stability Runs
Run in CI mode
CI=true npx playwright test

Run with retries
npx playwright test --retries=2

6. Reports & Artifacts
Generate HTML report
npx playwright show-report

Run with trace enabled
npx playwright test --trace on

Run with screenshots on failure
npx playwright test --screenshot=only-on-failure

Run with video on failure
npx playwright test --video=retain-on-failure

7. Environment Variables
Run with custom environment variable
ENV=staging npx playwright test

Headed only when needed
HEADED=true npx playwright test

8. Test Filtering & Control
Run only test.only
npx playwright test --forbid-only=false

Skip tests with .skip
npx playwright test --grep-invert "@skip"

Run tests by tag
npx playwright test --grep "@smoke"

9. Code Generation (Practice Tool)
Open Playwright codegen
npx playwright codegen https://example.com

Codegen with device
npx playwright codegen --device="Desktop Chrome"

10. Installation & Setup
Install Playwright
npm init playwright@latest

Install browsers
npx playwright install

Install Chromium only
npx playwright install chromium

11. Maintenance Commands
Clear Playwright cache
npx playwright install --force

Update Playwright
npm install @playwright/test@latest

12. Most Important Commands (Memorize These)
npx playwright test
npx playwright test --debug
npx playwright test --headed
npx playwright show-report
npx playwright codegen


If you can confidently explain when and why to use each of these, you are already operating at a strong SQA Automation Engineer level.